I thought this was delicious! Simple, ingredients that I normally have on hand and not just plain ol; boring steamed cabbage. I'm not much of a cooked cabbage fan to start with, but I really liked this dish and my husband said it was excellent! I left out the flour and used a little butter at that juncture and reduced it a little; wonderful side dish!

